PolicySet.Description: This Policy modifies the Capabilities response from a standard Geoserver to make the service compliant for OAuth2 Bearer Token use. The Permit decisions for the GetCapabilities request trigger an XSLT operation by the PEP to include the required ows:constraint elements. In order to process the Capabilities response according to the underlying schema, different XSLTs must be applied for 1) WMS 1.1.1 2) WMS 1.3.0 3) OWS Common 1.1 based services (WFS 2.0.0, WMTS 1.0.0) 4) OWS Common 2.0 based services (WCS 2.0.1 only?)
